<Body>                                             
<Title>印度发生假酒集体中毒事件 32人亡50人送医治疗</Title>
<ReportTime type="absTime">2013年10月19日 14:46　</ReportTime>
   来源：中国新闻网
<Content>   
<Paragraph>
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent">
<Participant sid="s1">中新网</Participant>
<Time tid="t1" type="relTime">10月19日</Time>
<Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter></Event>
<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent">
据
<Participant sid="s2">外媒</Participant>
<Time tid="t2" type="relTime">19日</Time>
<Denoter did="d2" type="statement">报道</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e3">
<Participant sid="s3">印度警方</Participant>
<Denoter did="d3" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e4">
<Time tid="t4" type="relTime">近日</Time>
，
<Location lid="l4">印度北部</Location>
发生假酒集体
<Denoter did="d4" type="emergency">中毒事件</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e5">
<Time tid="t5" type="relTime">目前</Time>
至少<Participant sid="s5">32人</Participant>
因饮用含有毒物质的自酿酒<Denoter did="d5" type="emergency">丧生</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e6">另有<Participant sid="s6" oid="o7">50人</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="perception">感到</Denoter>不适
</Event>
<Event eid="e7">被<Denoter did="d7" type="action">送</Denoter><Location lid="l7" type="destination">医</Location></Event>。
</Sentence></Paragraph>
<Paragraph>　　
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e8" type="thoughtevent">据<Denoter did="d8" type="statement">报道</Denoter></Event>
，<Event eid="e9" type="thoughtevent">
印度<Participant sid="s9">一名警官</Participant><Denoter did="d9" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e10">
<Participant sid="s10">这起事件</Participant>
<Denoter did="d10" type="action">发生</Denoter>在<Time tid="t10" type="relTime">周四(17日)</Time>
，地点在<Location lid="l10">北方邦阿桑加尔地区一处山村</Location></Event>
，
<Event eid="e11">
<Participant sid="s11,s12,s13,s14">数十村民</Participant>
在<Denoter did="d11" type="action">饮用</Denoter><Object oid="o11">一处商店买来的自酿酒</Object>后</Event>
，<Event eid="e12">感到<Denoter did="d12" type="perception">身体不适</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e13">被<Denoter did="d13" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l13" type="destination">当地医院</Location></Event>
<Event eid="e14">接受<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e15">
<Time tid="t15" type="relTime">截止目前</Time>
，已有<Participant sid="s15">32人</Participant>不治<Denoter did="d15" type="emergency">身亡</Denoter></Event>
，死者大多数是劳工。</Sentence></Paragraph>
<Participant>
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e16">
<Time tid="t16" type="relTime">目前</Time>还有<Participant sid="s16">50人</Participant>
在饮用“毒酒”后在
<Location lid="l16">医院内</Location><Denoter did="d16" type="operation">接受治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Participant>
<Paragraph
><Sentence>
<Event eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17,s18">当局</Participant>针对<Object oid="o17">此事</Object>展开
<Denoter did="d17" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>
，
<Event eid="e18">
并将<Participant oid="o18">8名政府官员</Participant>和<Participant oid="o18">4名警察</Participant>
暂时<Denoter did="d18" type="stateChange">停职</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Sentence>
<Event eid="e19" type="thoughtevent">分析<Denoter did="d19" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e20"><Location lid="l20">印度</Location><Time tid="t20" type="timeInterval">近年来</Time>
<Denoter did="d20" type="emergency">假酒中毒事件</Denoter>频发</Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence>为了增加酒的“烈度”，
<Event eid="e21">
<Participant sid="s21">没有取得酿酒执照的非法商家</Participant>
在酒中<Denoter did="d21" type="action">添加</Denoter><Object oid="o21">化学物质</Object></Event>
，往往损害人的健康，严重时可致人死亡。</Sentence></Paragraph></Content>
